YES IT WORKS!

It's not pre-patched so download patches from http://ss.softmodfiles.net

You will need the AUS PAL PFI, AUS PAL DMI and AUS PAL SS.

1. XDVDMulleter - Choose CRC Checking then click AutoFix.

2. Xbox Backup Creator - Choose Image Tools Tab then set the Xbox ISO Type to Xbox 360, and set the Action to Insert. Then simply click Security Sector and locate the AUS PAL SS file, then PFI Sector and locate the AUS PAL PFI file, and then DMI Sector and locate the AUS PAL DMI file.

3. XDVDMulleter - Choose CRC Checking then click AutoFix, then after this XDVDMulleter reports all Xtreme Compatability boxes checked!

Viola!
